metadata.name: Prince of Darkness
metadata.description:
prince of darkness  
we cast you down  
your wings are damaged  
your vibrations -  
felt  
lay down your lies  
let go your spear  
your words are honey  
honey does not die

Part of the "Honey Wings" Collection by Brendan S Bigney (The Nuclear Cowboy), Marine Corps Veteran, photographer, and Multi-Award-Winning Author.
